" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Odds ratios (95 percent CI) for outcomes of pregnancy in asthmatic vs control women in a large population based study",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\">",
